com.foreach.across.modules.entity.bind

Class DefaultEntityPropertyTemplateValueResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.entity.bind.DefaultEntityPropertyTemplateValueResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EntityPropertyTemplateValueResolver

    public class DefaultEntityPropertyTemplateValueResolver
extends Object
implements EntityPropertyTemplateValueResolver
    Default implementation of EntityPropertyTemplateValueResolver which checks if a resolver is registered as attribute on the property descriptor, and delegates to that one if it is.

    This implementation is attached as the default on an EntityPropertiesBinder and can be used as a base class.

    Since:
    3.3.0
    Author:
